cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is primarily focused on neural networks and their training, which falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the use of a cost function, which is related to machine learning and falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of convolutional layers, which is related to computer vision and falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a biologically plausible approach to deep learning, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
